N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 4 ยง 213.1 - Scope

State Regulations

This Part applies to exceptions and motions for leave to file
exceptions to the board to decisions, reports, orders, rulings or other
appealable findings or determinations of the director, the director of
conciliation, an assistant director or an administrative law
judge. Notes
